Package net.minecraft.world.entity.ai.memory

Class ExpirableValue<T>

java.lang.Object
net.minecraft.world.entity.ai.memory.ExpirableValue<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of expirable value that is held.
public class ExpirableValue<T>  extends Object
Represents an object with a value that expires after a certain amount of time.
